<refnamediv id="libclutter-glx-08-3-name"><refname>libclutter-glx-0.8</refname><refpurpose>Library for creating fast, visually rich and animated graphical user interfaces.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsect1 id="libclutter-glx-08-3-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para>
Clutter uses OpenGL (and optionally OpenGL ES for use on Mobile and embedded platforms) for rendering but with an API which hides the underlying GL complexity from the developer. The Clutter API is intended to be easy to use, efficient and flexible. 
</para>

<para>
Clutter support for media playback with GStreamer, Cairo graphics rendering, GTK+ embedding, via libclutter-gst, libclutter-cairo, and libclutter-gtk.
</para>

</refsect1>
